<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1152 nēṁṭi caitra ba<unclear>hu</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>la Aṣṭamiyu nādivāramunāṁḍu Āttilināṁṭilōpali vi 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>llūriśāsanuṁḍu<unclear>nu</unclear> Ājñavalkiśākhayuṁgāśyagōtruṁḍunu<unclear>nai</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>na viṁjarāju bejavāḍamallīśvaraśrīmahādēvaraku Akhaṁḍa
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dīpamunaku Iccina mēṁkkalu nalu<unclear>bhu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> nu 30 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēko
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ni prōlebōyyini koḍkulu Amarebōyuṁḍunuṁ carisenu
<lb n="7"/>yī dīpamunaku nitya māneṁḍu neyi putrānupautrika
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁbu Ācaṁdrārkkamu naḍapaṁggalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī
